<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Service Receipt</title>

<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  background:#f3f4f6;
  font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
  color:#111827;
}

.wrapper{
  padding:40px 12px;
}

.container{
  max-width:620px;
  margin:0 auto;
  background:#ffffff;
  border-radius:18px;
  overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:0 10px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
}

.header{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111827,#1f2937);
  padding:28px;
  text-align:center;
  color:#ffffff;
}

.header h1{
  margin:10px 0 0;
}

.badge{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:8px 14px;
  border-radius:999px;
  background:#ffffff;
  color:#111827;
  font-size:12px;
  font-weight:bold;
  letter-spacing:.08em;
}

.hero{
  padding:28px;
  text-align:center;
  background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#fff7cc,#ffe08a);
}

.hero img{
  width:240px;
  max-width:100%;
  border-radius:14px;
  display:block;
  margin:0 auto;
}

.content{
  padding:32px;
}

.content h2{
  margin-top:0;
}

.price{
  margin:24px 0;
  padding:22px;
  border-radius:14px;
  background:#f9fafb;
  border:2px dashed #d1d5db;
  text-align:center;
}

.value{
  font-size:34px;
  font-weight:700;
  color:#16a34a;
}

.footer{
  padding:18px;
  text-align:center;
  font-size:12px;
  color:#6b7280;
  background:#f9fafb;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="wrapper">
<div class="container">

<div class="header">
<div class="badge">SERVICE COMPLETED</div>
<h1>Your Receipt</h1>
</div>

<div class="hero">
<img src="https://media1.tenor.com/m/_2gmzwgSnLEAAAAd/hairdresser-barber.gif" alt="Man getting bald haircut">
</div>

<div class="content">

<h2>Hello, {{name}} 👋</h2>

<p>
Your appointment has been successfully completed.
Looks like the barber went all in today 😄
</p>

<div class="price">
<div>Total Amount</div>
<div class="value">֏{{price}}</div>
</div>

<p>
Thank you for choosing us. We look forward to seeing you again soon.
</p>

<p><strong>Fresh cut. Clean style. Legendary result.</strong></p>

</div>

<div class="footer">
© 2026 Your Company. All rights reserved.
</div>

</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>